Description: Rock Creek Dental Center are your local Invisalign, Dental Implants, Cosmetic Dentistry, and Tooth Whitening specialists in Rockville, MD.
Headquarters Regions: Washington DC Metro Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Rock Creek Dental Center is the premier provider of dental services in Rockville, Maryland. The firm offers a wide range of dental care, diagnosis, and treatment services that meet the highest standards for quality and excellence. The Center’s main area of specialization is cosmetic dentistry.   Opened in 1998, Rock Creek quickly became one of the most respected names in the dental care industry, with a reputation that soon spread to other cities all over the state. Today, Rock Creek Dental Center remains the foremost specialist dental clinic in Maryland, with a renown built largely on its expertise in the field of cosmetic dentistry.   Rock Creek employs a team of top-flight dentists and dental technicians, all of whom have extensive experience in most every aspect of cosmetic dentistry. Rock Creek dentists utilize the latest and most sophisticated dental technologies in order to deliver the highest quality of services possible. It is this team that enables Rock Creek to handle everything from simple teeth bleaching and whitening to more advanced dental procedures with ease and professionalism.   Rock Creek’s dental team is headed by Dr. Paige Gaznavi, herself one of the most respected names in the dental profession. After earning her Bachelor of Arts and Sciences degree from George Mason University in Virginia, Dr. Gaznavi went on to doctorate studies in the Dental Surgery at Baltimore's University of Maryland School of Dental Medicine.   The next stage of Dr. Gaznavi’s training involved a General Practice residency at Maimonides Medical Center in Brooklyn, New York. It was during this period that she learned the value of individualized dental care and patient comfort, both of which she aims to provide to Rock Creek’s patients to this very day.   One of the cornerstones upon which Rock Creek’s services are built is patient care. Most patients are understandably apprehensive about the prospect of getting treatment, to the extent that they will avoid it as long as possible. Because early and immediate dental care is essential for achieving optimal results, Rock Creek provides patients with a range of options that alleviate their concerns with regard to getting dental care in a timely manner.   Rock Creek Dental Center’s range of services includes dental implants, cosmetic dentistry, Invisalign procedures, toothache treatment, and tooth whitening. Each of these services have been developed in order to address the needs of Rockville residents for state-of-the-art skin care and treatment, and they are delivered with the professionalism and attention to detail that has made Rock Creek the top dental care provider in the region.   Today, nearly twenty years after Rock Creek first opened its doors, the clinic remains committed to delivering the same quality services that has become the earmark of its success. Dr. Paige Gaznavi and her team are committed to providing the best dental care possible, and every effort is made to stay updated in the latest advances in dental technology. With continuing training and recertification, Dr. Gaznavi works to ensure that Rockville, Maryland residents have access to the finest dental care services available.   Rock Creek Dental Center is located at 5542 Norbeck Road in Rockville, Maryland.

DM3 enables the integration of multiple sensors to coordinate security systems through a simple Graphical User Interface and initiates communication and data-driven messaging between systems and to emergency personnel. Defentect Group, Inc. develops and provides IP based alerting system that protects against chemical, biological, radiological, nuclear, and explosive threats. The company offers DM3, a software platform that enables the integration of multiple sensors to coordinate security systems through a simple graphical user interface and initiates communication and data-driven messaging between systems and to emergency personnel; and DefenCall, an iPhone application which links to DM3 and creates a mobile personal safety device and service. Full Description: Orbital Overview is revolutionizing the field of meteorological technology, setting a new standard in weather forecasting with its user-focused, accuracy-driven approach. Our platform, powered by NOAA's API, employs device coordinates for hyper-localized weather data, delivering precision that surpasses traditional city-based forecasts. What truly sets us apart in the industry is our commitment to accessibility. We offer an expansive 100 hours of detailed hourly weather forecasts completely free of charge, a significant leap from the industry norm where competitors often restrict their 40+ hour forecasts behind a paywall. This feature empowers our users with comprehensive, reliable weather insights without any cost. Our sophisticated suite includes state-of-the-art Doppler radar and infrared satellite technology, providing an in-depth analysis of weather patterns. Along with this, users have access to extensive 7-day forecasts, ensuring a complete overview of upcoming weather conditions. The platform doesn't just stop there. We provide daily high and low temperature readings, current conditions (temperature, text-based weather descriptions, rain probability, relative humidity, wind direction, speed), and the specific time of the forecast, all designed for utmost accuracy and user convenience. Completing our range of services is FastCast – a quick, efficient tool for obtaining immediate weather forecasts for any specified city and state. This feature is particularly user-friendly, offering essential weather information rapidly and succinctly. Orbital Overview is more than just a weather forecasting company; we are at the forefront of technological advancement, with an eye towards a sustainable future for our planet and ambitious plans for space exploration. Our mission is to redefine how humanity interacts with and understands the environment, both here on Earth and beyond, through innovative and freely accessible technology.
